@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vleygh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((tmp + 0.69 * v1 + 0.49)))
    tmp = 0.71
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v2 + 0.76) - tmp))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = ((v0 + wp.exp(v2 + 0.42)) * ((v2 + 0.61 / v2 + 0.01) / (tmp + 0.06 + tmp + 0.27)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs((v2 + 0.10 * v0 + 0.66)))
    data[tid] = v0
